high_descs: Go straight and then take lefts to go towards the inner side of the counters towards the stoveburner.
Pick up the pot off the stove.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Place the pot into the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Place the pot into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cool a pot in a fridge and place it into a sink.

high_descs: Walk ahead and enter the kitchen on the left to face the stoveburner.
Pick up the pot from the stove.
Walk to the fridge on the left.
Cool the pot in the bottom shelf of the fridge and take the pot out.
Turn around to walk to the sink.
Place the pot on the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cold pot on the sink.

high_descs: Walk around to the other side of the counter, past the refrigerator, to the other side of the stoveburner.
Pick up the pot off of the stove.
Turn to the left and move to the fridge.
Chill the pot inside the bottom section of the refrigerator, closing the door, then take the chilled pot back out.
Turn around and move to the end of the counter on the side of the sink.
Place the cooking pot to the upper right of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cooking pot on the sink.
